Version 0.4
 - Fixed zombie processes creation when more than one
   client disconnects in a short period of time.

Version 0.3
 - Support for RAW UDP (MUDP) streams

Version 0.2
 - Fix address in use when two clients wanted same
   source mRTP stream.
 - Changed configfile and commandline options
   resolving order so commandline opts do override
   configfile defaults.

Version 0.1
 - Initial release
